text:
Grapevine: 'Downton Abbey' final season announced Detroit rocker Rikki St. James dies, Drew Lane leaves Greater Media, Muse comes to town and more entertainment news. Check out this story on detroitnews.com: http://detne.ws/1RT7E99 Actors Joanne Froggatt, from left, Michelle Dockery and Hugh Bonneville speak during the "Downton Abbey" panel at the PBS 2015 Summer TCA Tour held at the Beverly Hilton Hotel, in Beverly Hills, Calif.
 Detroit News.
